175 A.3d 167 J.T., PLAINTIFF-PETITIONER, v. NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, DEFENDANT-RESPONDENT.

C-334 September Term 2017

078749 November 17, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-4942/5335-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
